  <div class="about-hero-content">
    <h1>Experience Elevated Yachting Aboard<br>Knot Caught Slippin</h1>
    <p class="about-hero-tagline">A 66-foot 2024 Azimut Magellano designed for refined comfort, effortless elegance, and unforgettable experiences on the water.</p>
  </div>
